net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.postprocess
Class BundleProcessingStatus

java.lang.Object
  net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.postprocess.BundleProcessingStatus

public class BundleProcessingStatus
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates the status of a bundling process. It is meant to let postprocessors have metadata available about the processed data

Author:
Jordi Hernández Sellés, Ibrahim Chaehoi
